Retrieve the user-defined variable names

Source: R/user_defined.R
user_defined_variables.Rd

Function to retrieve the names of the additional output variables that can be defined in x13 and tramoseats with the parameter userdefined.

user_defined_variables(sa_object = c("X13-ARIMA", "TRAMO-SEATS"))

Arguments

sa_object

a character: "X13-ARIMA" to retrieve the additional output variables available for the X13-ARIMA method and "TRAMO-SEATS" for the TRAMO-SEATS method.

Examples

user_defined_variables("X13-ARIMA")
